headline: Cintas (NasdaqGS:CTAS) Announces CFO Transition As Shares Dip 6%
summary: Cintas (NasdaqGS:CTAS) has been in the spotlight with the transition in its executive team, as Mike Hansen's retirement and Scott Garula stepping in as CFO signal a focus on strategic continuity. Despite a turbulent market environment marked by significant declines across major indices due to global trade tensions, Cintas shares managed a 2% price move over the last quarter.
